item.title: 2014: Year In Review
item.description: Even after spending a few days attempting to transcribe my feelings and emotions, I still feel that this post doesn’t even come close to conveying how important this year has been to me. I traveled to two states, graduated from college, met a plethora of new people, hiked a 13-mile trail, visited the beautiful parks of Big Sur and Muir Woods, saw Linkin Park in concert, and finished two commercial games…just to name a few.
